Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.57,0:00:05.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說過世間萬物都有著靈魂 這樣的說法嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.49,0:00:09.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論什麼 只要被珍惜的使用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.60,0:00:12.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,見習神仙愛心蛋 就會從中誕生哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.62,0:00:14.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可是秘密事項喲！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.09,0:00:21.59,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,愛心蛋嘰裡咕嚕滾下來 與大家來相見！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.59,0:00:24.10,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,砰砰敲出了…小神仙!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.10,0:00:27.52,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,實現吧 大家的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.52,0:00:30.69,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}實現？個蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.98,0:00:34.97,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好想要告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.97,0:00:37.99,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,（但但但是 不可以啊）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.99,0:00:40.93,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是有點被察覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.93,0:00:43.98,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,（這這這啊 最重要了）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.98,0:00:46.66,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是第一次有了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.66,0:00:53.00,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不能說的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.00,0:00:55.96,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,要～怎麼辦啊～～～！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.96,0:00:59.42,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,愛心蛋嘰裡咕嚕滾下來 最愛你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.42,0:01:02.01,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,（嗨嗨 最愛你了 嗨嗨）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.01,0:01:05.37,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,愛心蛋嘰裡咕嚕滾下來 和睦友好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.37,0:01:08.06,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,（嗨嗨 你叫什麼呢?）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.06,0:01:14.06,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,真心的珍惜 世界煥然一新
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.06,0:01:17.32,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,愛心蛋嘰裡咕嚕滾下來 最愛你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.32,0:01:20.07,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,（嗨嗨 最愛你了 嗨嗨）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.07,0:01:23.32,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,愛心蛋嘰裡咕嚕滾下來　永遠在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.32,0:01:26.08,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,（嗨嗨 看著我嘛 嗨嗨）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.08,0:01:28.95,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,勇敢的心兒永不言敗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.95,0:01:35.00,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,將有趣的夢想化為現實 一起來玩吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.00,0:01:37.75,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,砰砰敲出了…小神仙!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.75,0:01:40.95,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,實現吧 大家的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.95,0:01:43.84,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}實現？個蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.24,0:22:30.47,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(330,0)}好運？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.47,0:22:35.70,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,乓乓乓 乓乓乓 乓乓乓!（嗨!）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.70,0:22:38.37,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,乓乓乓 乓乓乓 乓乓乓!（咦…?）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.37,0:22:40.77,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}乓乓乓 乓乓乓！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.35,0:22:45.11,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,七色繽紛的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.11,0:22:47.57,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,（扣扣塔嘛! 扣扣塔嘛!）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.57,0:22:50.28,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,美美的閃閃發光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.28,0:22:51.49,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,（扣扣塔嘛!）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.49,0:22:56.91,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,感謝你真心的愛著我們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.91,0:23:02.79,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,想為你而實現
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.79,0:23:05.58,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,（吶吶一起來、唱吧!）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.58,0:23:10.96,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,尾巴甩甩 扣扣塔嘛!（哇!）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.96,0:23:13.09,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,在蛋殼裡藏著許許多多
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.09,0:23:15.84,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,的夢·想（嗨! 嗨!）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.84,0:23:18.18,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,尾巴甩甩 扣扣塔嘛!（哇!）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.35,0:23:21.10,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,尾巴甩甩 實現的話!（哇!）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.10,0:23:26.06,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,心兒也有會大大的感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.06,0:23:29.86,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,NICO NICO的咪咪笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.36,0:23:44.08,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(206,666)}啊 啊… 一直要在一起!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.36,0:23:44.08,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1066,616)}（乓乓乓 乓乓乓 乓乓乓!）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.08,0:23:47.50,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,350)}（乓乓乓 乓乓乓... 胖次?）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.88,0:01:58.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛心蛋、翱翔天際
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.74,0:02:03.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 小誠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.73,0:02:05.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於送來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.50,0:02:07.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.09,0:02:11.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 鯉魚旗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.67,0:02:15.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兒童節?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.63,0:02:16.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.90,0:02:20.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是祝願所有的孩子能夠幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.73,0:02:25.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最初是祈願男孩子能夠健康成長的節日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.20,0:02:28.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像莎莎說的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.06,0:02:32.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 來 這是給男孩子們的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.90,0:02:39.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 感覺強而有力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.69,0:02:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自從在電視上看了 就很嚮往啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.20,0:02:45.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武士們披甲戴盔 上戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.61,0:02:50.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來一決勝負 塗之助
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.00,0:02:53.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來戰吧 笑丸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.32,0:02:59.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕莉妮也戴上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.61,0:03:01.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 我也要？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.54,0:03:03.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好帥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.77,0:03:05.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很襯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.32,0:03:08.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別 別一直看著我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.68,0:03:12.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 心彩 來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.11,0:03:14.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.67,0:03:16.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我稍微去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.24,0:03:17.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.36,0:03:20.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 風力適合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.94,0:03:23.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 現在開始升鯉魚旗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.98,0:03:25.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.44,0:03:29.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.84,0:03:34.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次見到那麼大的魚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.22,0:03:38.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是暢遊天空的魚 也就是鯉魚...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.16,0:03:40.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暢遊天空的魚!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.45,0:03:41.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.79,0:03:44.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塗之助 去逮住那魚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.46,0:03:46.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下明白 笑丸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.21,0:03:49.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吞撻也務必一同前往
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.59,0:03:52.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕莉妮衛門 你也來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.01,0:03:54.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要去？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.32,0:03:57.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢著 我還沒解說完
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.64,0:04:00.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.74,0:04:08.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 湊近了看 更大了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.29,0:04:16.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道那是神秘的巨大生物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.09,0:04:19.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定會被吃掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.43,0:04:21.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 這貨很老實啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.61,0:04:26.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是肚子餓扁了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.22,0:04:29.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吞撻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.51,0:04:31.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪拿來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.15,0:04:33.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 突擊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.03,0:04:34.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.92,0:04:48.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裡面也很寬敞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.82,0:04:50.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是什麼都沒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.33,0:04:52.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.14,0:04:53.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.77,0:04:58.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,諸位 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.14,0:05:09.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,升起來了 升起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.13,0:05:12.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.61,0:05:16.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.49,0:05:18.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吃柏餅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.80,0:05:27.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清爽的風
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.61,0:05:33.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鯉魚旗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.55,0:05:42.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.95,0:05:44.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.44,0:05:50.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 你們誰偷吃柏餅了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.69,0:05:51.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.86,0:05:53.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少了兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.13,0:05:55.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.57,0:05:56.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.02,0:05:58.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.36,0:06:00.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 反正有不少 無所謂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.71,0:06:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.16,0:06:10.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕了 塗塗他們泡到鯉魚旗裡面去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.01,0:06:14.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那鯉魚旗被風吹跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.45,0:06:15.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.13,0:06:24.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在天上飛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.59,0:06:25.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無與倫比的美景
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.07,0:06:29.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飛吧 飛吧 直到雲上面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:32.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是掉下去了 怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.25,0:06:34.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會掉下去？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.82,0:06:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從這裡掉下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.77,0:06:45.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那還真要命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.32,0:06:48.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柏餅會摔癟的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.21,0:06:51.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.00,0:06:53.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.50,0:07:00.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.85,0:07:02.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全追不上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.49,0:07:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從風向來看 接著會往南去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.44,0:07:07.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先趕過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.92,0:07:08.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:11.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想想辦法 想想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.77,0:07:14.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好勒 用我的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:18.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尾巴甩甩 愛心蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.99,0:07:23.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好運 好運 好運來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.74,0:07:30.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就不會掉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.40,0:07:38.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有不好的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.46,0:07:46.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑笑又遇到了危機
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.63,0:07:49.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吞撻把柏餅給烏鴉吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.43,0:07:51.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.43,0:08:02.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.97,0:08:10.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小希 我去試航一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.49,0:08:12.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要飛太遠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.27,0:08:13.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞭解 我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.13,0:08:18.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平衡稍微不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.44,0:08:21.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還需要調整一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.67,0:08:23.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.80,0:08:27.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心彩 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.56,0:08:29.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vivid
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.78,0:08:31.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:33.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我飛到天上去找
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.24,0:08:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.50,0:08:38.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也帶上我 會有作用的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.08,0:08:40.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 上來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.68,0:08:42.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們馬上追上來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.20,0:08:48.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vivid 大家被吹到南邊去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.68,0:08:50.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往南飛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:51.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.11,0:08:53.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.39,0:08:57.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:08:58.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莎莎 Vivid
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.84,0:09:00.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快救我們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.80,0:09:03.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然的 但是沒法一次帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.27,0:09:05.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這飛機最多還能載一個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.13,0:09:07.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.62,0:09:12.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不得已 救援的基礎就是先從最弱小的開始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.28,0:09:14.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個一個來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.71,0:09:16.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那先救我...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.40,0:09:21.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡先走的話 以後就會被當成最弱雞的了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.99,0:09:26.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要忍住 這才是男子漢 這才是武士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.26,0:09:31.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先走的話 大家說不定會遭殃的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.81,0:09:37.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我與柏餅算兩人份 不捨得放下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.78,0:09:40.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別管我 笑笑你先走（小傑聲線?）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.78,0:09:46.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下沒問題 膽小的帕莉妮你先走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.49,0:09:49.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我不能先跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.04,0:09:51.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吞撻 你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.10,0:09:56.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 無法丟下這孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.97,0:10:00.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰先走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.46,0:10:03.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武士要留到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.41,0:10:05.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們先請
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.24,0:10:07.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:09.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1037,147)\fscx511\fscy250}●
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:09.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fscx150\fscy150\pos(996,171)}●
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:09.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fscy100\pos(980,180)}●
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:09.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fscx50\fscy50\pos(968,185)}●
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:09.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1036,105)}MDZZ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.24,0:10:09.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點決定！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.37,0:10:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那帶上我的柏餅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.71,0:10:13.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.52,0:10:14.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你搞嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.05,0:10:17.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送柏餅下去 還不如送我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.70,0:10:18.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.19,0:10:20.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.64,0:10:24.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柏餅摔癟了就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.92,0:10:26.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們才糟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.66,0:10:28.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.48,0:10:30.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別煽風點火
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.38,0:10:31.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.53,0:10:33.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.20,0:10:34.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之我先走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.73,0:10:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.69,0:10:38.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是醜陋 何等的醜陋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.26,0:10:41.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才的烏鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.87,0:10:44.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又有不好的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.63,0:10:53.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.51,0:11:01.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是澡堂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.92,0:11:05.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕莉妮愛乾淨的心情起作用了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.94,0:11:07.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.08,0:11:11.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是笑笑說要抓魚 才會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.98,0:11:14.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塗塗不也是很來勁嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.15,0:11:23.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於能悠哉的吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.14,0:11:33.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備怎麼辦 那幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.80,0:11:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母親節大作戰！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.04,0:11:59.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子媽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:02.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 孩子爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.30,0:12:04.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶爾也兩個人去看電影吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:06.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.51,0:12:09.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是還要打掃 整理庭院
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.19,0:12:10.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還要做飯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:11.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個先放一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.15,0:12:13.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶爾也像以前約會那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.46,0:12:17.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.39,0:12:18.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一路順風
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.14,0:12:20.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 心彩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.00,0:12:22.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看家就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.48,0:12:23.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.11,0:12:31.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 要忙起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.44,0:12:32.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是母親節
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.37,0:12:34.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母親節？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.80,0:12:36.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什麼節
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.43,0:12:38.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感謝媽媽的節日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.79,0:12:43.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓每天都為了家人努力的媽媽個放鬆一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.90,0:12:47.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和小誠來打掃 做家務
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.32,0:12:50.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心彩好偉大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.58,0:12:54.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們為了小美裡也出點力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.34,0:13:00.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人要代替小美裡是很累的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.29,0:13:02.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忙東忙西 絕對會暈的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.98,0:13:07.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對對 忙到連愛心蛋的手都要借一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.14,0:13:11.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該說是連貓的手都要借
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.14,0:13:14.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 就拜託你們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.42,0:13:18.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那從哪做起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.99,0:13:23.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先配合媽媽回來的時間 來親手做麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.11,0:13:28.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是光看教材有點沒底
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.66,0:13:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吞撻拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.64,0:13:32.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.90,0:13:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先攪拌材料
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.17,0:13:38.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接著和麵團
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.74,0:13:42.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加入黃油 拍打
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.85,0:13:43.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.69,0:13:52.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做麵包好吃力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.73,0:13:55.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們能幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.09,0:14:05.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和大家一起做 很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.34,0:14:08.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發面大概要1小時
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.49,0:14:10.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還不能烤嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.28,0:14:16.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這叫發酵 等一會的話 會變得更好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.71,0:14:19.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁空檔來打掃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.58,0:14:20.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.29,0:14:34.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽真不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.07,0:14:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要做的事那麼多 永遠都做不完吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.63,0:14:42.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽這麼忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.61,0:14:44.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.85,0:14:48.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 小美裡太偉大了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.87,0:14:50.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 說的是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.06,0:14:54.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有時發怒很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.33,0:14:57.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是很溫柔 很可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.08,0:15:01.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心彩最喜歡小美裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.25,0:15:02.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.43,0:15:04.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以今天要努力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.72,0:15:09.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啦啦啦 謝謝你 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.25,0:15:12.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最最最喜歡了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.60,0:15:19.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直 一直 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.13,0:15:24.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝 美蘿莉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.93,0:15:27.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好勒 剩下的掃除就包給我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.92,0:15:30.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心彩再休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.55,0:15:34.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心彩接著還要烤麵包吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.70,0:15:36.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休息的時候就好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.72,0:15:40.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就稍微嬌一回
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.99,0:15:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.26,0:15:59.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.47,0:16:01.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花買回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.14,0:16:03.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放在樓下了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.49,0:16:04.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.00,0:16:06.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去打掃房間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.54,0:16:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.77,0:16:13.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3點了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.12,0:16:16.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸帶媽媽去看電影
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.30,0:16:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 大概3點回來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.98,0:16:21.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是3點啊 明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.20,0:16:26.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 還沒固形
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.94,0:16:31.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 打電話給爸爸 再拖延一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.31,0:16:37.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 這種時候居然沒帶手機（也算日文冷笑話...）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.16,0:16:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心彩怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.14,0:16:42.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽馬上要回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.83,0:16:46.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在開始烤的話 至少要30分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.05,0:16:50.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明都準備好了 跟爸爸約好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.52,0:17:01.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心彩 我們去拖小美裡30分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.86,0:17:04.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 不行 很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.94,0:17:07.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事 會注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.07,0:17:11.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和吞撻來幫心彩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.49,0:17:14.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家齊心協力 就能辦到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.06,0:17:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒... 謝謝大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.93,0:17:21.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 任務開始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.07,0:17:26.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,電影很有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.87,0:17:28.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.11,0:17:30.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發現倆人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.59,0:17:33.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會走哪條路回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.81,0:17:37.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倆人會穿過公園 回四葉家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.58,0:17:39.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.47,0:17:47.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早料到了 從超王牌愛心蛋特工代號346那 得到了機密情報
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.58,0:17:52.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}{\fs30}與媽媽約會大作戰\N10點20分 連媽媽出門（微笑）\N10點55分 在意大利餐廳吃飯\N12點10分 看電影（注意確認3D眼鏡）\N13點45分 電影結束
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.92,0:17:50.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的約會行程嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.63,0:17:52.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.48,0:17:56.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼先去公園埋伏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.16,0:18:04.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但要怎麼讓他們多停一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.34,0:18:10.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽喜歡音樂 在公園辦歌會留住他們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.99,0:18:13.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就交給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.53,0:18:29.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好歡快的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.53,0:18:42.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麥克風故障了吧
