Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.70,0:19:21.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.11,0:19:23.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再麻煩也要上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.61,0:19:25.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狗狗來挖這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.47,0:19:34.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個節奏是趕不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.36,0:19:39.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿曼達拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.04,0:19:41.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來幫幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.63,0:19:43.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喵喵來挖這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.76,0:19:45.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿曼達
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.38,0:19:51.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.37,0:19:57.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近心彩吃的...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.35,0:20:00.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,施工中？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.44,0:20:03.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個可愛的工地
