Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.57,0:20:13.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就爭取到不少時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.69,0:20:16.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心彩的麵包烤好了沒？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.85,0:20:26.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.79,0:20:29.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.21,0:20:31.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任務結束
