Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.37,0:20:43.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.01,0:20:45.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母親節的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.32,0:20:47.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.44,0:20:50.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.85,0:20:53.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有花與賀卡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.45,0:21:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.42,0:21:18.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心彩 媽媽很開心真太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.08,0:21:21.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 多虧了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.34,0:21:24.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.21,0:21:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心彩 化妝台 浴室 連廚房的角落都打掃乾淨了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.62,0:21:33.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很累吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.34,0:21:36.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不只是我 還有愛...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.53,0:21:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 雖然很累
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.97,0:21:42.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望媽媽能輕鬆一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.73,0:21:52.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.60,0:21:58.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能成為心彩和小誠的媽媽 我很開心
